      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Usable fair-condition driver being sold as-is. This is a presentable car that can be enjoyed and driven, but it shows clear signs of age with noticeable cosmetic wear, imperfections in the finish, and an interior that is serviceable rather than fresh. It appears to have been maintained well enough to stay on the road, but buyers should expect an older vehicle with flaws and some needs rather than a clean showpiece. A straightforward, honest option for someone looking for a driver-quality example at a realistic price.",
