      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical choice for a buyer looking for affordable transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows clear signs of age and wear, but it still offers real value at an accessible price point. If you want a low-cost option with room to make it your own, this is one worth a look.",
