    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels or a solid little project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly option with plenty of life left for the right buyer. Great for someone handy, a first project, or just a low-cost commuter to get from A to B without spending big. Priced to sell and worth a look if you want affordable transportation with potential.",
