      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with a strong-running powertrain, responsive automatic shifting, and a chassis that still feels composed on the road. The engine pulls cleanly, starts reliably, and the car has clearly benefited from routine upkeep over its life. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present, and it\u2019s best approached as an honest used vehicle rather than a showpiece, but for someone wanting dependable transportation or a capable platform to sort and improve, this one offers a lot of value. Priced to move and well-suited for a buyer who appreciates a mechanically sound car with visible character.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car now. Not pretty, but it gets the job done. Priced to move fast.",
